{"tid":1200532,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"唯唯 約定你地今晚金鐘見喇！","createTime":"2019-06-10T18:35:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T06:21:30.000Z","uid":90522,"like":97,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"08c5c6257f0f53d4dbbd309d42fce9bc6987ca5c","tid":1200532,"uid":90522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:35:35.000Z","msg":"發夢前日中左胡椒噴霧<br />\n第一個幫我洗眼既竟然係唯唯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲叫我唔好衝動  有咩事佢呢D大隻既衝先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住我地做左朋友傾左好耐計<br />\n知道左好多秘密<br />\n原來當年年初一夜晚<br />\n佢都在場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等我地仲一路怪佢<br />\n<br />\nbtw<br />\n佢仲爆左d花邊新聞比我聽<br />\n原來佢一直都好憎樂小姐同其他公司高層<br />\n話佢地成日扮曬野,迫人陪食飯<br />\n為左生計先被迫要擦鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講左一陣佢就出左去衝<br />\n衝之前仲同我講6月11晚再見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到我興奮到依家都訓唔著<br />\n好期待再見到你啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"829659ad9aad0647200034d8ceba6469aee5bc93","tid":1200532,"uid":50835,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:37:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/at1y1Nk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fat1y1Nk.jpg&h=282257f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3dcb5c82f3857238ef3334d1ee491065bc2eb0fe","tid":1200532,"uid":90522,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:37:12.000Z","msg":"原來佢叫開樂小姐「臭西玲」<br />\n次次聽到都笑到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d15775a6fe1b6f41cf69a7821d67653f1910647f","tid":1200532,"uid":82327,"